    tmp = 0.95
    v2 = (0.49 + v0)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v2 + 0.89) * v0))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.14 - v1 + 0.45) + tmp))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.23 - tmp + 0.99)) - wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.53)))
